a5cd4ddd13cb"],

Cell["\<\
The analytic result for an interior maximum under log-utility is the optimal \
policy [see Eqs. (11.10) and (10.18) in the paper]\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9732453825793467`*^9, 3.973245500226101*^9}, {
  3.9751654256022863`*^9, 3.975165478424*^9}, {3.978737518684156*^9, 
